title: Evan Wivell from Mindset and React Records
itunes:title: Evan Wivell from Mindset and React Records
description:
This week I speak with Evan Wivell who is the vocalist from the hardcore band Mindset as well as the owner of React! Records. We discuss what it's like being raised in a very rural area, architecture and the concept of "giving back" to the music scene.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
